OL,3,GDumfries, Galloway, Lothian & Borders
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA dry morning with sunny spells
OL,6,Fin the west but cloudier in the east.
OL,7,FCloudy across all parts in the
OL,8,Fafternoon with the chance of the odd
OL,9,Fshower.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FCloudy start to the evening
OL,12,Fwith isolated showers dying out and
OL,13,Fclear intervals developing. Dry
OL,14,Fovernight with clear spells in the
OL,15,Fwest, cloudier with a light shower
OL,16,Fpossible in east.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
